WEBVTT

00:03.969 --> 00:04.790
Hut one!

00:04.900 --> 00:05.870
Hut two!

00:05.990 --> 00:09.440
High!
Come on, come on! Get open!

00:10.470 --> 00:12.120
Inception!

00:12.400 --> 00:13.940
Touchdown!

00:17.220 --> 00:19.550
We did it, yay!

00:21.900 --> 00:23.570
Pathetic.

00:23.630 --> 00:25.570
Playing all by yourself.

00:25.640 --> 00:27.570
Get some friends, kid.

00:27.640 --> 00:30.370
I'm all in.

00:32.040 --> 00:34.080
Fold.
[Grunts]

00:34.140 --> 00:36.550
I'm never playing
with you again.

